model potentials and diverse electronic structure methods, as listed
in <xref rid="tbl1" ref-type="other">Table <xref rid="tbl1" ref-type="other">1</xref></xref>. The choice
of each one depends on the specific problem, always requiring a trade-off
between quality and computational costs. The third-party programs
are not distributed with Newton-X.</p>
